===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg-y|jimm|y}}

# (''slang'') A [[marijuana]] [[cigarette]].
# (''in plural'' '''jimmies''') Candy [[sprinkle]]s.
# A device used to circumvent a locking mechanism; a [[slim-Jim]].
# Slang for penis. Many rap songs use this slang, such as Boogie Down Productions "Jimmy", Bell Biv Devoe "Do Me". Also, a condom can be referred to as a "jimmy hat". This term was used in the movie [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/CB4 CB4], and several rap songs including "Giving up the Nappy Dugout" by Ice Cube.

